Both whole transcriptome and ribosome profiling raw counts were inter-replica (intra-condition) normalized for the relative library size with the size factors computed by the DESeq2 library of the bioconductor package in R [41].We used the RR-score [11] used for lncRNAs. \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
